INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(213, 1, '2011-02-19 15:27:33', '2011-02-19 22:27:33', 'The Ahwatukee Healing Rooms operate under the umbrella of Within His Presence Ministries, Rev. Bob Severdia, Director.\r\n\r\nWe are Members of the International Association of Healing Rooms (IAHR) headquartered in Spokane, Washington, under the direction of Cal Pierce.\r\n\r\nBob &amp; Janet Severdia are also IAHR AZ State Advisors/Directors for region 8 (Southern California, Arizona &amp; New Mexico).\r\n\r\n<strong>Who are We?</strong>\r\n\r\nThe Ahwatukee Healing Rooms provide a loving, safe, confidential environment where you can come to receive healing prayer. Some are healed instantly by a miraculous touch from God. Other receive their healing progressively over a period of days, weeks or months. We are committed to pray for you for as long as it takes, contending for your healing until you are completely well!\r\n\r\nWe minister salvation, physical healing and emotional healing to the complete person (spirit, body and soul).\r\n\r\n<strong>Who Prays?</strong>\r\n\r\nOur Healing Room team consists of over twenty-five Christians from more than four churches in the Ahwatukee region. The Healing Rooms are rooms full of the love of God and His presence to heal physically, emotionally, mentally and spiritually through loving, gifted and committed servants of our Lord Jesus Christ.\r\n\r\nEach ministering worker must have a release from their pastor to qualify, as well as an interview with the Directors. Each member of the team has been through an intensive training process, starting with a three month commitment to serving in the Healing Rooms.\r\n\r\nA family atmosphere of love and unity permeates the Healing Rooms, even though our home churches are as diverse as Assembly of God, Baptist, Foursquare, Nazarene, Presbyterian, Roman Catholic, Vineyard, and various independent fellowships.\r\n\r\n<strong>Jesus the Healer</strong>\r\n\r\nWe believe, as Hebrews 13:8 states, that:\r\n\r\n"Jesus Christ is the same yesterday, today and forever".\r\n\r\nWhile He walked the earth He healed the sick, the poor in spirit and the brokenhearted, cast out demons and performed many miracles. We believe He is the same today and still does these things. We pray with that understanding and in the powerful name of Jesus. We believe according to Isaiah 53:4-5, that Jesus paid for our healing on the cross.\r\n\r\n<strong>Healing Rooms around the World</strong>\r\n\r\nThere are many members of the IAHR around the world. If you are looking for a Healing Room in another location, you can refer to the International Directory at <a href="http://www.healingrooms.com">www.healingrooms.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Endorsements</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>IAHR</li>\r\n	<li>Joan Hunter Ministries</li>\r\n	<li>Four Corners Alliance</li>\r\n	<li>Expected End Ministries</li>\r\n	<li>Identity Network</li>\r\n	<li>Life Worship Ministries</li>\r\n</ul>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '2-revision-12', '', '', '2011-02-19 15:27:33', '2011-02-19 22:27:33', '', 2, 'http://www.ahwatukeehealingrooms.com/uncategorized/2-revision-12', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
